order of deployment:
1. saltstack master -- will be used to automate everything else
2. wireguard
3. docker swarm
4. traefik

## deployment steps:

salt master init:
1. wget https://repo.saltproject.io/bootstrap/stable/bootstrap-salt.sh
2. ./bootstrap-salt.sh -P stable 3007.1 (this installs salt-minion too)

wireguard init:
1. run wireguard salt state
2. 




note: for client wireguard setup, check if its behind a NAT, and if thats the case, set wiregaurd's persistantkeepalive to 25 seconds




lastly: migrate hub to openbsd
